Special Arrows				KEY:Special Arrows ~ Pixie	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural				DEFINE:SpecialArrowDC|0			DESC:As a free action, when a pixie fires an arrow from any bow, it can decide to change the arrow’s properties by sprinkling it with magical pixie dust.	SOURCEPAGE:p.228		BONUS:VAR|SpecialArrowDC|10+(HD/2)+CHA		BENEFIT:When a pixie fires an arrow from any bow, it can decide to change the arrow’s properties by sprinkling it with magical pixie dust. Doing so is a free action as long as the pixie is the one who fires the arrow. A pixie can use this dust %1 times each day. The dust is useless to another creature unless the pixie gives the dust freely. In this case, the pixie chooses what effect the dust will have on an arrow when it is applied, and it takes a standard action to apply the dust to the arrow. Once pixie dust is applied to an arrow, the pixie’s chosen effect persists on the arrow for only 1 round. As long as an arrow is altered in this way, it does not inflict damage when it hits; it only causes its new effect. A pixie can choose any one of the following three effects when dusting an arrow, Charm, Memory Loss or Sleep.|CHASCORE		ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(charm, memory loss or sleep arrows)
Special Charm Arrow			KEY:Charm ~ Pixie			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural																													DESC:Charm; The target must succeed on a DC %1 Will save or be affected as though by a Charm Monster spell for 10 minutes.|SpecialArrowDC	SOURCEPAGE:p.228
Special Memory Loss Arrow	KEY:Memory Loss ~ Pixie		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural																													DESC:Memory Loss; The target must succeed on a DC %1 Will save or be affected by a modify memory spell. This effect can only eliminate the previous 5 minutes of memory—a pixie typically uses this ability to make the target forget it encountered the pixie so it won’t chase the pixie when he flees.|SpecialArrowDC	SOURCEPAGE:p.228
Special Sleep Arrow			KEY:Sleep ~ Pixie			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural																													DESC:Sleep; The target must succeed on a DC %1 Will save or fall asleep for 5 minutes.|SpecialArrowDC	SOURCEPAGE:p.228
